  <div class="container">
    <h1>üö® Safe Sakhi SOS</h1>
    <p>Emergency help for women & children</p>

    <button class="btn btn-call" onclick="callPolice()">
      üìû Call Police (112)
    </button>

    <button class="btn btn-whatsapp" onclick="sendWhatsApp()">
      üí¨ WhatsApp SOS Message
    </button>

    <button class="btn btn-location" onclick="sendLocation()">
      üìç Send Live Location
    </button>

    <div class="note">
      If you are in danger, press any button immediately.
